	*POSSESS <monster-name>

	This command allows you to assume the identity of the named monster.
You can speak through the monster, and when you move, the monster mimics
your actions.  The monster does not take on any of your characteristics.
It retains its own hitpoints and magicpoints.   The command is a toggle,
and is also used to release the monster.



:*possess nobleman
You possess a nobleman.
